<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Crusaders Resplendent</title>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>

  <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", media: "all" %>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-primary">
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Crusaders Resplendent</a>
      <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
        <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
      </button>
      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
        <ul class="navbar-nav">
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link active" href="#">Home</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" href="#">Chapter History</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Jumbotron -->
  <header class="jumbotron text-center text-white d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="background: url('https://images4.alphacoders.com/290/290118.jpg') no-repeat center center; background-size: cover; height: 400px;">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="display-3">Crusaders Resplendent</h1>
      <p class="lead">"In the Emperor’s Light, We Shine"</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row text-center">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>Chapter History</h3>
        <p>
          Founded in the aftermath of the Horus Heresy, the Crusaders Resplendent trace their lineage to the Imperial Fists. Their history is one of unyielding resilience, bound by a sacred duty to protect the Imperium’s borders from the alien and the heretic.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>Fighting Doctrine</h3>
        <p>
          The Crusaders Resplendent are known for their masterful siege tactics and impeccable defensive fortifications. Drawing inspiration from their primogenitor Chapter, they stand immovable in the face of overwhelming odds, turning strongholds into impenetrable bastions of Imperial might.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>Heroes of the Chapter</h3>
        <p>
          Chapter Master Aurelius Vorn, a legend among Space Marines, has led countless crusades. Captain Decimus of the 1st Company is known for single-handedly holding a vital pass against a Tyranid onslaught, earning him the title "The Shield Eternal."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="mt-5 py-3 bg-dark text-white">
    <div class="container d-flex justify-content-between">
      <span>© 2025 Crusaders Resplendent</span>
      <a href="#" class="text-white text-decoration-none">Home</a>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <!-- Bootstrap JavaScript -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
